<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Opciones Avanzadas - Usuarios</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1477346611705-65d1883cee1e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-4">
    
    <div id="reloj-vivo" class="fixed top-4 right-4 bg-gray-800 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md shadow-lg font-mono text-xl font-bold z-50 border border-gray-700">
        00:00:00
    </div>
    <script>
        function actualizarReloj() {
            const ahora = new Date();
            const horas = String(ahora.getHours()).padStart(2, '0');
            const minutos = String(ahora.getMinutes()).padStart(2, '0');
            const segundos = String(ahora.getSeconds()).padStart(2, '0');
            document.getElementById('reloj-vivo').textContent = `${horas}:${minutos}:${segundos}`;
        }
        actualizarReloj();
        setInterval(actualizarReloj, 1000);
    </script>

    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full max-w-4xl">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-purple-800 mb-6">Opciones Avanzadas</h1>

        {{#successMessage}}
        <div class="bg-green-100 border border-green-400 text-green-700 px-4 py-3 rounded relative mb-4" role="alert">
            <span class="block sm:inline">{{successMessage}}</span>
        </div>
        {{/successMessage}}

        {{#errorMessage}}
        <div class="bg-red-100 border border-red-400 text-red-700 px-4 py-3 rounded relative mb-4" role="alert">
            <span class="block sm:inline">{{errorMessage}}</span>
        </div>
        {{/errorMessage}}

        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <table class="min-w-full bg-white">
                <thead class="bg-purple-100 border-b border-purple-200">
                    <tr>
                        <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-purple-800 font-bold">ID</th>
                        <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-purple-800 font-bold">Nombre de Usuario</th>
                        <th class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-purple-800 font-bold">Tipo de Cuenta</th>
                        <th class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-purple-800 font-bold">Administrador</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {{#usuarios}}
                    <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-100">
                        <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600">{{id}}</td>
                        <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-800 font-semibold">{{name}}</td>
                        <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">{{tipoCuenta}}</td>
                        <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center">
                            <input type="checkbox" disabled {{#isAdmin}}checked{{/isAdmin}} class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-600 bg-gray-100 border-gray-300 rounded focus:ring-purple-500 cursor-not-allowed">
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    {{/usuarios}}
                    
                    {{^usuarios}}
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="4" class="py-4 text-center text-gray-500">No hay usuarios registrados.</td>
                    </tr>
                    {{/usuarios}}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-red-200 shadow-inner">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-red-700 mb-4">Eliminar un Usuario</h2>
            
            <form action="/admin/usuarios/borrar" method="post" class="space-y-4">
                <div>
                    <label for="user_id" class="block text-gray-800 text-sm font-medium mb-2">Seleccione el usuario que desea eliminar del sistema:</label>
                    <select id="user_id" name="user_id" required class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500 bg-white">
                        <option value="" disabled selected>-- Desplegar lista de usuarios --</option>
                        {{#usuarios}}
                            <option value="{{id}}">ID: {{id}} - {{name}} ({{tipoCuenta}})</option>
                        {{/usuarios}}
                    </select>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-yellow-100 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-4 mt-4">
                    <p class="text-sm text-yellow-800"><strong>Advertencia:</strong> Esta acción es irreversible. Si elimina una cuenta de tipo "Profesor", también se borrarán todos sus datos académicos asociados.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="flex gap-4 mt-6">
                    <a href="/dashboard" class="w-1/2 bg-gray-500 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-600 text-center transition duration-300 flex items-center justify-center">
                        Cancelar y Volver
                    </a>
                    <button type="submit" class="w-1/2 bg-red-600 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-md hover:bg-red-700 transition duration-300 font-bold shadow-md">
                        Eliminar Definitivamente
                    </button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-blue-200 shadow-inner mt-8">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4">Otorgar Permisos de Administrador</h2>
            
            <form action="/admin/usuarios/hacer-admin" method="post" class="space-y-4">
                <div>
                    <label for="admin_user_id" class="block text-gray-800 text-sm font-medium mb-2">Seleccione el usuario al que desea hacer Administrador:</label>
                    
                    <select id="admin_user_id" name="admin_user_id" required class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 bg-white">
                        <option value="" disabled selected>-- Elegir un usuario común o profesor --</option>
                        
                        {{#usuarios}}
                            {{^isAdmin}}
                                <option value="{{id}}">ID: {{id}} - {{name}} ({{tipoCuenta}})</option>
                            {{/isAdmin}}
                        {{/usuarios}}
                    </select>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-blue-100 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4 mt-4">
                    <p class="text-sm text-blue-800"><strong>Nota:</strong> Al otorgar este permiso, el usuario tendrá acceso total a esta pantalla y podrá gestionar profesores y usuarios.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="flex mt-6">
                    <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-blue-600 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 transition duration-300 font-bold shadow-md">
                        Hacer Administrador
                    </button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
        </div>
</body>
</html>